{"talk":{"id":60081,"name":"Alexandra Auer: The intangible effects of walls","description":"More barriers exist now than at the end of World War II, says designer Alexandra Auer. And when you erect one wall, you unwittingly create a second -- an \"us\" versus \"them\" partition in the mind that compromises our collective safety. With intriguing results from her social design project focused on two elementary schools separated by a fence, Auer encourages us to dismantle our biases and regain perspective on all the things we have in common.","slug":"alexandra_auer_the_intangible_effects_of_walls_apr_2020","recorded_at":"2019-02-01 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-04-03 20:18:10","updated_at":"2020-12-20 18:33:06","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":626,"name":"TEDxEindhoven"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/ed3c29b7546432e1a5ef38383cb2a846d2438900_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/ed3c29b7546432e1a5ef38383cb2a846d2438900_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/ed3c29b7546432e1a5ef38383cb2a846d2438900_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/ed3c29b7546432e1a5ef38383cb2a846d2438900_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/50f6f5f5fda977efd013d6ae8996bf6df816642b_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AlexandraAuer_2019X-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":5873598,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AlexandraAuer_2019X-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":16222883,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AlexandraAuer_2019X-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":28787694,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450k":{"uri"